(44, 12, 7, 44, 16, 26, 26, 'chains fell off from his hands', 'Divine Intervention in Prisons', 'Both passages emphasize miraculous events leading to the release of prisoners. In Acts 12:7, an angel frees Peter, while in Acts 16:26, an earthquake causes chains to fall off. This connection highlights the theme of divine intervention in dire circumstances.', 'theme', 0.44699999999999995, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
