(44, 12, 7, 19, 146, 7, 7, NULL, 'Loosening of Prisoners', 'Both passages emphasize the act of freeing prisoners. Acts 12:7 describes Peter''s chains falling off, while Psalms 146:7 states, ''The Lord looseth the prisoners.'' This connection highlights a theme of divine intervention for those in captivity.', 'theme', 0.37, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
