(44, 12, 10, 4, 15, 34, 34, NULL, 'Imprisonment and Release Motif', 'This connection highlights the theme of being in ward or prison, as seen in both passages. In Acts, Peter is held in ward but is miraculously released, while in Numbers, a man is put in ward awaiting a decision.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
